## 3. CRM Template (AirTable Structure)

### Required Columns

| **Column Name** | **Type** | **Purpose** | **Example** |
|----------------|---------|------------|------------|
| **Contact Name** | Text | Full name | "John Smith" |
| **Title** | Text | Job title | "VP Offshore Operations" |
| **Company** | Text | Organization | "Shell Energy" |
| **Segment** | Single Select | Customer archetype | "Offshore Energy", "Maritime Fleet", "Aquaculture" |
| **Role Bias** | Single Select | Buying influence | "Buyer", "User", "Influencer", "Blocker" |
| **LinkedIn URL** | URL | Profile link | https://linkedin.com/in/... |
| **Email** | Email | Contact email | john.smith@shell.com |
| **Phone** | Phone | Contact number | +1-xxx-xxx-xxxx |
| **Outreach Date** | Date | When contacted | 2026-01-20 |
| **Outreach Method** | Single Select | Channel used | "LinkedIn", "Email", "Phone", "Referral" |
